items.headline: Flash on over to the Flash Gordon Wikia
items.desc: The Flash Gordon Wikia is a community driven fan site that allows anybody to contribute and add information about Flash Gordon. The goals of the Flash Gordon Wikia are to be a complete resource for anything having to do with the Flash Gordon universe. From the comics to the characters to the movies and a lot more. Please join us in our efforts to continually make this a better resource for Flash Gordon.
